2000-12-04 19:26:10  Rev 901    perdig

	* :
	  - changed game's _ggzcore_confio_parse and file_parser to accept a 
	  autocreate
	    argument
	  - made the game autocreate a config file if it doesn't exist (call
	    _ggzcore_confio_parse w/ autocreate = 1)
